Package at.nineyards.anyline.modules.ocr

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AnylineOcrBaseListener
    A base result listener for the Anyline OCR module with all none UI relevant callbacks.
    AnylineOcrListener
    A result listener for the Anyline OCR module
    AnylineOcrUiListener
    A listener for UI relevant events that can be used with AnylineOcrHelper.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnylineOcrConfig
    A class used to configure the Anyline OCR module
    AnylineOcrHelper
    A helper class for AnylineOcr that works without a view.
    AnylineOcrResult
    A Result container for the simple ocr module
    AnylineOcrScanView
    The AnylineOcrScanView can be used to recognize text.

    Enum Description
    AnylineOcrConfig.ScanMode
    The possible scan modes see AnylineOcrConfig.setScanMode(ScanMode)
    AnylineOcrError
    An enum of possible causes for an aborted run for the SimpleOcr module.
